{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"Today, more than half\nof the world's population lives in cities."},{"time":6000,"text":"The urbanization process\nstarted in the late 1700s"},{"time":9880,"text":"and has been increasing since then."},{"time":12200,"text":"The prediction is that by 2050,"},{"time":15280,"text":"66 percent of the population\nwill live in cities"},{"time":18320,"text":"and the United Nations,\nthe World Health Organization,"},{"time":21880,"text":"the World Economic Forum, are warning us,"},{"time":25360,"text":"if we don't plan\nfor the increased density,"},{"time":28080,"text":"current problems in our cities,\nlike inequality, congestion, crime"},{"time":33200,"text":"can only get worse."},{"time":34600,"text":"As a result, urban planners\nand city developers"},{"time":37240,"text":"are putting a lot of effort and creativity"},{"time":40800,"text":"in designing our future,\ndenser, bigger cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45720,"text":"But I have a different opinion."},{"time":47600,"text":"I think urbanization is actually\nreaching the end of its cycle,"},{"time":51640,"text":"and now people are going to start\nmoving back to the countryside."},{"time":55800,"text":"And you may think,\n\"But what about the trend?\""},{"time":58840,"text":"Well, let me tell you,"},{"time":60840,"text":"socioeconomic trends don't last forever."},{"time":64239,"text":"You know, 12,000 years ago"},{"time":65960,"text":"everybody was perfectly happy"},{"time":69000,"text":"roaming the land, hunting and gathering."},{"time":72040,"text":"And then, the trend changes,"},{"time":74720,"text":"and the new thing\nis to live in a farm and have cattle,"},{"time":78200,"text":"until it changes again."},{"time":80040,"text":"When we get to the industrial revolution."},{"time":83520,"text":"Actually, that is what started\nthe urbanization process."},{"time":87120,"text":"And you know what triggered it?"},{"time":89520,"text":"Steam power, machines,"},{"time":92800,"text":"new chemical processes --"},{"time":94640,"text":"in two words, technological innovation."},{"time":99360,"text":"And I believe technology\ncan also bring the end of this cycle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103520,"text":"I've been working on innovation\nfor most of my career."},{"time":106480,"text":"I love it. I love my job."},{"time":108640,"text":"It allows me to work with drones,\nwith 3D printers and smart glasses,"},{"time":112760,"text":"and not just those you can buy in the shop\nbut also prototypes."},{"time":116840,"text":"It's a lot of fun sometimes."},{"time":120000,"text":"Now, some of these technologies"},{"time":121880,"text":"are opening new possibilities\nthat will radically change"},{"time":125000,"text":"the way we did things before"},{"time":126800,"text":"and in a few years,"},{"time":128800,"text":"they may allow us\nto enjoy the benefits of city life"},{"time":132720,"text":"from anywhere."},{"time":134400,"text":"Think about it."},{"time":135640,"text":"If you could live in a place\nwith a lower crime rate"},{"time":139440,"text":"and more space"},{"time":140800,"text":"and a lower cost of living"},{"time":142560,"text":"and less traffic,"},{"time":144680,"text":"of course many people would want that,"},{"time":146960,"text":"but they feel they don't have a choice."},{"time":149680,"text":"You have to live in the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153120,"text":"Well, in the past,\npeople moved to the cities"},{"time":155800,"text":"not because they loved the city itself"},{"time":158400,"text":"but for the things\nyou could have in a city,"},{"time":161080,"text":"more job opportunities,"},{"time":162920,"text":"easier access to services and goods"},{"time":165000,"text":"and a rich social life."},{"time":167040,"text":"So let's dive deeper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169800,"text":"More jobs and career opportunities."},{"time":173120,"text":"Is that still true today,"},{"time":174480,"text":"because the office people\nare starting to realize"},{"time":177680,"text":"that working in the office\nand being in the office"},{"time":181680,"text":"may not be the same thing anymore."},{"time":184280,"text":"According to a study\nby Global Workplace Analytics,"},{"time":187440,"text":"more than 80 percent of the US workforce\nwould like to work from home."},{"time":192680,"text":"And do you know how much it costs\nfor a company to even have an office?"},{"time":197240,"text":"11,000 dollars per employee per year."},{"time":201800,"text":"If only half of those workers"},{"time":204600,"text":"would telework\neven 50 percent of the time,"},{"time":208040,"text":"the savings in the states\nwould exceed 500 billion dollars,"},{"time":212880,"text":"and it could reduce greenhouse gases\nby 54 million tons."},{"time":217680,"text":"That is the equivalent"},{"time":218960,"text":"of 10 million cars\noff the streets for a whole year."},{"time":224320,"text":"But even though most people\nwould want to telework,"},{"time":227600,"text":"current technology\nmakes the experience isolating."},{"time":231160,"text":"It's not comfortable."},{"time":232440,"text":"It doesn't feel like being there."},{"time":234800,"text":"But that is going to change"},{"time":237400,"text":"by the convergence of two technologies:"},{"time":239720,"text":"augmented reality and telepresence robots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243600,"text":"Augmented reality already today"},{"time":245600,"text":"allows you to take your office\nenvironment everywhere with you."},{"time":249160,"text":"All you need is a wearable computer,\na pair of smart glasses,"},{"time":252680,"text":"and you can take your emails\nand your spreadsheets"},{"time":255080,"text":"with you wherever you go."},{"time":257240,"text":"And video conferences and video calls\nhave become very common these days,"},{"time":261880,"text":"but they still need improvement."},{"time":264320,"text":"I mean, all those little faces\non a flat screen,"},{"time":268080,"text":"sometimes you don't\neven know who is talking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270600,"text":"Now, we already have something\nway better than static videocalls:"},{"time":275440,"text":"your average telepresence robot."},{"time":278120,"text":"I call it tablet on a stick."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281106,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":282280,"text":"You can control, you can move around,"},{"time":285040,"text":"you can control what you're looking at."},{"time":287240,"text":"It's way better, but far from perfect."},{"time":291160,"text":"You know how they say"},{"time":292400,"text":"that most human\ncommunication is nonverbal?"},{"time":296000,"text":"Well, the robot doesn't\ngive you any of that."},{"time":298760,"text":"It looks like an alien."},{"time":302200,"text":"But with advances in augmented reality,"},{"time":305040,"text":"it will be easy to wrap the robot\nin a nice hologram"},{"time":308520,"text":"that actually looks\nand moves like a person."},{"time":312520,"text":"That will do it."},{"time":314360,"text":"Or else, forget the robot."},{"time":316440,"text":"We go full VR,"},{"time":318440,"text":"and everybody meets in cyberspace."},{"time":321400,"text":"Give it a couple of years\nand that will feel so real,"},{"time":324920,"text":"you won't tell the difference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327280,"text":"So what was the next reason\nwhy people move to cities?"},{"time":331080,"text":"Access to services and goods."},{"time":333840,"text":"But today you can do all that online."},{"time":337080,"text":"According to a study made by comScore,"},{"time":340400,"text":"online shoppers in the US last year"},{"time":342800,"text":"did more than half\nof their retail purchases online,"},{"time":347200,"text":"and the global market for e-commerce"},{"time":350560,"text":"is estimated to be\nat two trillion dollars."},{"time":354560,"text":"And it's expected to reach 2.38\nby the end of 2017,"},{"time":359800,"text":"according to eMarketer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362600,"text":"Now, from a logistics standpoint,"},{"time":365240,"text":"density is good for deliveries."},{"time":368520,"text":"Supplying goods\nto a shopping mall is easy."},{"time":371840,"text":"You can send big shipments to the shop,"},{"time":374520,"text":"and people will go there, pick it up\nand take it home themselves."},{"time":377680,"text":"E-commerce means we need to ship onesies"},{"time":380360,"text":"and have them home delivered."},{"time":382160,"text":"That's more expensive."},{"time":383440,"text":"It's like the difference between\nhaving a birthday party for 20 people"},{"time":387160,"text":"or bringing a piece of the cake"},{"time":389280,"text":"to each of your 20 friends at their place."},{"time":393240,"text":"But at least in the city,"},{"time":395400,"text":"they live close to each other."},{"time":396880,"text":"Density helps."},{"time":398920,"text":"Now, e-commerce deliveries\nin the countryside,"},{"time":403160,"text":"those take forever."},{"time":405680,"text":"The truck sometimes needs to drive miles\nbetween one address and the next one."},{"time":410160,"text":"Those are the most expensive\ndeliveries of all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415040,"text":"But we already have a solution for that:"},{"time":417640,"text":"drones."},{"time":419080,"text":"A vehicle carrying a squadron of drones."},{"time":422480,"text":"The driver does some of the deliveries"},{"time":424360,"text":"while the drones are flying\nback and forth from the truck as it moves."},{"time":427720,"text":"That way, the average cost\nfor delivery is reduced,"},{"time":430280,"text":"and voila:"},{"time":432800,"text":"affordable e-commerce services\nin the countryside."},{"time":436840,"text":"You will see:"},{"time":438200,"text":"the new homes of our teleworkers"},{"time":439960,"text":"will probably have\na drone pod in the yard."},{"time":443640,"text":"So once the final mile delivery\nis not a problem,"},{"time":446240,"text":"you don't need to be in the city\nto buy things anymore."},{"time":450080,"text":"So that's two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451320,"text":"Now, what was the third reason\nwhy people move to cities?"},{"time":454560,"text":"A rich social life."},{"time":456800,"text":"They would need to be\nin the city for that these days."},{"time":459360,"text":"Because people these days,"},{"time":461440,"text":"they make friends,\nthey chat, gossip and flirt"},{"time":464840,"text":"from the comfort of their sofa."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":468040,"text":"And while wearing their favorite pajamas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471800,"text":"There are over two billion\nactive social media users in the world."},{"time":476560,"text":"In a way, that makes you think\nlike we are connected"},{"time":479880,"text":"no matter where we are."},{"time":481120,"text":"But OK, not completely."},{"time":483440,"text":"Sometimes you still need\nsome real human contact."},{"time":487880,"text":"Ironically, the city,\nwith its population density,"},{"time":491800,"text":"is not always the best for that."},{"time":494760,"text":"Actually, as social groups become smaller,"},{"time":497800,"text":"they grow stronger."},{"time":499440,"text":"A recent study made in the UK"},{"time":501680,"text":"by the Office for National Statistics"},{"time":503840,"text":"showed a higher life satisfaction rating"},{"time":506720,"text":"among people living in rural areas."},{"time":510040,"text":"So as people settle in the countryside,"},{"time":513320,"text":"well, they will buy local groceries,"},{"time":516320,"text":"fresh groceries, foodstuff,"},{"time":518159,"text":"maintenance services."},{"time":520280,"text":"So handymen, small workshops,\nservice companies will thrive."},{"time":526000,"text":"Maybe some of the industrial\nworkers from the cities"},{"time":528480,"text":"displaced by the automation"},{"time":530760,"text":"will find a nice alternative job here,"},{"time":533120,"text":"and they will move too."},{"time":535880,"text":"And as people move to the countryside,"},{"time":537760,"text":"how is that going to be?"},{"time":539440,"text":"Think about autonomous,"},{"time":542240,"text":"off-the-grid houses with solar panels,"},{"time":544320,"text":"with wind turbines\nand waste recycling utilities,"},{"time":548880,"text":"our new homes producing their own energy\nand using it to also power the family car."},{"time":554120,"text":"I mean, cities have always been regarded\nas being more energy-efficient,"},{"time":558240,"text":"but let me tell you,"},{"time":559520,"text":"repopulating the countryside\ncan be eco too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564680,"text":"By now, you're probably thinking\nof all the advantages of country living."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":571280,"text":"I did it myself."},{"time":572560,"text":"Six years ago, my wife and I,\nwe packed our stuff,"},{"time":576120,"text":"we sold our little apartment in Spain,"},{"time":578080,"text":"and for the same money\nwe bought a house with a garden"},{"time":583200,"text":"and little birds that come\nsinging in the morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":587280,"text":"It's so nice there."},{"time":589880,"text":"And we live in a small village,\nnot really the countryside yet."},{"time":592880,"text":"That is going to be my next move:"},{"time":595080,"text":"a refurbished farmhouse,"},{"time":597320,"text":"not too far from a city, not too close."},{"time":600200,"text":"And now we'll make sure\nto have a good spot for drones to land."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":604640,"text":"But hey, that's me."},{"time":606400,"text":"It doesn't have to be you,"},{"time":607680,"text":"because it would seem\nlike I'm trying to convince somebody"},{"time":610440,"text":"to come join us in the country."},{"time":611960,"text":"I'm not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":614600,"text":"I don't need more people to come."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":618120,"text":"I just think they will"},{"time":619920,"text":"once they realize they can have\nthe same benefits the city has."},{"time":624076,"text":"But if you don't like the country,"},{"time":625720,"text":"I have good news for you, too."},{"time":627880,"text":"Cities will not disappear."},{"time":630640,"text":"But as people move out,"},{"time":631920,"text":"a lower density will help them\nrecover a better flow and balance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637280,"text":"Anyway, I guess now\nyou have some thinking to do."},{"time":641960,"text":"Do you still think\nyou need to live in the city?"},{"time":644280,"text":"And more importantly,"},{"time":646520,"text":"do you want to?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648800,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650040,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}